QuestData.Title: Defending Your Title
QuestData.Description: Everyone's impressed by your performance, sister. But do not let your guard down -- every new challenger with delusions of grandeur is going to come out swinging for your title of Hyldskvinnar.$B$BShow these upstarts what you're made of.
QuestData.LogDescription: Gretta the Arbiter in Brunnhildar Village wants you to defeat 6 Victorious Challengers.
QuestData.RewardText: You continue to prove yourself worthy. We are honored by your presence.
